@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v0 = (v0 / wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.42)))
    v2 = (v2 / wp.abs(wp.abs(v2 + 0.25)))
    v1 = 0.68
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.62)) - wp.exp((tmp + 0.18 + tmp + 0.82)))
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.46 / v0 + 0.82) - 0.49) / wp.sin((v2 + 0.36 + v0 + 1.00)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.45 + v0 + 0.21)))
    data[tid] = v0
